      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Process</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-methods field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Methods:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/methods/online-consultations">Online Consultations</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/methods/crowdsourcing">Crowdsourcing</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitated field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facilitation?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Yes</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If yes, were they ...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_facilitation_type%3A170">Professional Facilitators</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_facilitation_type%3A171">Peer Facilitators (i.e. other participants not professional facilitators)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-method field-type-list-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facetoface, Online or Both:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Face-to-Face</div><div class="field-item odd">Online</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-communication-mode field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Interaction among Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A9">Discussion, Dialogue, or Deliberation</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Decision Method(s)?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="f